Description: Provides templates, formatting tools, and 'ggplot2' themes
    tailored for the Accessible Teaching, Learning, and Assessment Systems
    (ATLAS) organization. These templates facilitate the creation of topic
    guides and technical reports, while the formatting functions enable
    users to customize numbers and tables to meet specific requirements.
    Additionally, the themes ensure a uniform visual style across
    graphics.
